{"tid":707329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為發公開信 「會遵守每個國家法律」","createTime":"2018-06-18T14:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T02:06:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"31fde08a41174b130983d5254461a6bb5a7cc345","tid":707329,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"華為發公開信 會遵守每個國家法律<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1868174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1868174&d=DEPrfqq5BVsZqc%2FvWm%2F6rJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=1bdeb87a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1868174</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲媒體報道，當地情報機構建議不要將華為納入5G設備供應商名單，主要是憂慮採用華為的電訊設備可能危及國家安全。華為向澳洲政府發出公開信反擊，稱這種觀點過於片面。<br />\n<br />\n華為澳洲主席John Lord及兩名董事在公開信中稱，最近圍繞着中國問題的公開評論，提到華為在澳洲扮演的角色，引發一些關於安全的顧慮，惟許多評論都過於片面，沒有以事實為基礎。<br />\n<br />\n華為在信中又稱，該公司是一家<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立公司</span>，在已開展業務的170個國家中，<span style=\"color: red;\">會遵守每一個國家的法律和準則</span>，否則其生意一夜之間就會結束。"},{"pid":"56aeba29b191069c93453044b226b5a1b3ea1674","tid":707329,"uid":85168,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"冇意思，佢要遵守中國法律，就會違反大多數西方國家嘅法律"},{"pid":"10213b751c5a8edc84d424c0f0a1b52238f5970e","tid":707329,"uid":27146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"留名睇生意一夜結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95704088698952862de40a3392c2f3e33eab51f","tid":707329,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:42:14.000Z","msg":"首先，佢係一間支那公司"},{"pid":"91f164034cee5dff5b8fd74ee9159e8e313b91d6","tid":707329,"uid":13663,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/224309_ea